name: "Out of the dark into the light" by The Majority
description:
Debut EP "Out of the dark into the light" by The Majority. Includes "The Windowframe", "Sooner or later" ( 2008 re edit ) "Amsterdam" "If i knew" ( 2008 re edit ) and "My Last Breath" Recorded at Crash Studios, Liverpool, United Kingdom 2008. Free DVD of The Window Frame and extra footage with every order for limited period.

The p+p stated is for the United Kingdom only. For all other destinations contact The Majority for further information
